ColorAid Project
================
Hello, the project it's a free iPhone application for help person that have some color vision deficiency.
inability or decreased ability to see color or perceive color differences.
The project try to use image symbol from (http://www.coloradd.net created by Miguel Neiva) and music note 
(from Harbisson's Sonochromatic Scales http://www.enotes.com/topic/Eyeborg)

Thanks to Matt Gemmell,Dave DeLong,Amudi SEBASTIAN,Matt Gallagher,Tommy Szalapski and Tevac Forum for code components,
math and ideas.

Please let me know your suggestions and comments about this work.

Thanks,
Francesco Germinara
www.germinara.it
